    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the Story</h2><br>Marty has crash landed on an alien world. He must escape, but can he survive? The mysterious inhabitants of the world hunt him at every turn. Guide Marty to discover what happened to the abandoned human colony. The planet holds a dark secret and you must choose how to resolve it... Find your answers by scanning the environment for clues, solving puzzles and searching unique environments. All while while battling alien creatures, and rogue robots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744610/extras/f6ee60a32a09e67f9bc3f3f9fa75f47c.poster.avif?t=1739857834\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744610/extras/f6ee60a32a09e67f9bc3f3f9fa75f47c.webm?t=1739857834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744610/extras/f6ee60a32a09e67f9bc3f3f9fa75f47c.mp4?t=1739857834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Discover secrets and power up Marty</strong> to explore deeper into the planet Xenix in this metroidvania style first person adventure game. <br></li><li><strong>Collect dozens</strong> of power-ups to go from fragile to super charged over the course of the adventure.<br></li><li><strong>Explore a mysterious alien world</strong> with 4 different environments to discover.<br></li><li><strong>Recover</strong> logs and piece together the fate of the missing colonists.<br></li><li><strong>Fight off</strong> dozens of alien life forms including titanic battles with MegaFauna.<br></li><li><strong>Solve complex puzzles</strong> using unique power ups including self duplication.<br></li><li>The game can be <strong>played with tips</strong> for a more comfortable experience.<br></li><li>Featuring <strong>different possible endings</strong> based on choices made by the player in the game.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744610/extras/b4e156519fb08eb1ef55a4cb2d849d4b.poster.avif?t=1739857834\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744610/extras/b4e156519fb08eb1ef55a4cb2d849d4b.webm?t=1739857834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744610/extras/b4e156519fb08eb1ef55a4cb2d849d4b.mp4?t=1739857834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Group Combat</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Why fight alone when you can <strong>team up with yourself</strong>?!<br></li><li>Marty will gain the ability to duplicate himself, making himself into a <strong>one robot army!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Confuse your enemies</strong>, unsure of which version of you is the real one.<br></li><li>With this ability you can <strong>record and duplicate actions</strong>. Create synergistic actions that work together to topple enemies and solve puzzles.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744610/extras/1680b3f2cba9864c5de81e59d486fcaa.poster.avif?t=1739857834\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744610/extras/1680b3f2cba9864c5de81e59d486fcaa.webm?t=1739857834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744610/extras/1680b3f2cba9864c5de81e59d486fcaa.mp4?t=1739857834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenges Missions</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Special challenges will <strong>put your skills to the test</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>New challenges are added regularly </strong> so check in to see whats new.<br></li><li>See how you rank against the world with<strong> competitive leader boards</strong>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Split Screen Multiplayer</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fight 1v1</strong> for points by accomplishing pre-selected objectives.<br></li><li><strong>Deaths creates clones</strong> for your army so matches escalate with each death. <br></li><li>1v1 becomes 2v2... 5v5... 50v50... and so on... as each life is recorded and added to the battle turning you into a literal one man army!</li></ul>",
